    public abstract class AbstractTableView<S extends DataSeries<?>,I extends Data>
extends AbstractUnmodifiableDataTable<S>
implements DataListener, TableView
    Base class for DataTable views that are (optionally) based on another DataTable.

    O. J. Coleman

        public int getRowKeyIndex()
        Description copied from interface: DataTable
        Returns the index of the series that represents the row keys, or -1 if there is no such series. By default this is set to the first series added that contains String values. The row key is used in the DataTable.transpose() operation.

      • update

        public void update(DataEvent cause)
        Description copied from interface: View
        Update this view. If the view does not cache the data it presents then it may not be necessary to do anything in this method. Note that views based on a Data or subclasses thereof will generally update themselves automatically when the underlying DataSet changes. This method is for handling the case where the view is also affected by an external factor, such as parameters to a function that may change.
        Specified by:
        update in interface View
        Parameters:
        cause - The event that triggered the update, or null if not applicable.
